# Note that my external keyboard has a dip switch in it so that it works
# properly with the Mac:
#
# - On a Mac keyboard modifiers on left are: Control / Option (Super) / Command
# - On a Windows keyboard modifiers are: Control / Windows (Super) / Alt
# - On Linux the modifiers are: Control / Super / Alt
#
# In other words, "Alt" here means "Command (Super)", not actual "Option
alt + space
  dmenu_run -l 10 -fn SourceCodePro:pixelsize=34
